text: chaur anak( mou ham meat) pol tha brasenbae puok anak leak bang avei del mean nowknong chetd robsa puok anak ryy puok anak leatatradeang vea a l laoh pitchea doeng vea . haey trong doeng nouv avei del mean now leumekh cheachraen chean ning avei del mean now leu phendei . haey a l laoh mean anoupheap leu avei teangoasa
